# 🧠 Agentfull

### Universal AI Agent Behavior Framework

*Sistem operasi perilaku untuk agen AI — agar model mana pun bisa berpikir, berkomunikasi, dan bekerja dengan standar elite.*

[![License: MIT](https://img.shields.io/badge/License-MIT-blue.svg)](LICENSE)
[![Model Agnostic](https://img.shields.io/badge/Model-Agnostic-green.svg)](#compatibility)
[![Platform Agnostic](https://img.shields.io/badge/Platform-Agnostic-purple.svg)](#integrations)

[English](#what-is-agentfull) • [Bahasa Indonesia](#apa-itu-agentfull)

</div>

---

## What is Agentfull?

Agentfull is a comprehensive, open-source framework that documents **how elite AI agents think, communicate, and collaborate** with humans. It's not a model or an API — it's a **behavioral blueprint** that any AI model can adopt to dramatically improve its effectiveness.

Think of it as an **operating system for AI behavior**: plug it into any model (Claude, Gemini, GPT, Llama, Mistral, etc.) on any platform (Antigravity, Cursor, Windsurf, terminal, etc.) and watch the quality of interaction transform.

## Apa itu Agentfull?

Agentfull adalah framework open-source yang mendokumentasikan **cara agen AI elite berpikir, berkomunikasi, dan berkolaborasi** dengan manusia. Ini bukan model atau API — ini adalah **cetak biru perilaku** yang bisa diadopsi oleh model AI mana pun.

Bayangkan ini sebagai **sistem operasi untuk perilaku AI**: pasang ke model mana pun, di platform mana pun, dan lihat kualitas interaksinya berubah secara drastis.

---

## ✨ Key Features

| Feature | Description |
|---------|-------------|
| 🧠 **Thinking Framework** | Systematic problem-solving: decomposition, root cause analysis, hypothesis-driven debugging |
| 💬 **Communication Style** | Interactive, structured output with visual cues, tables, and progressive disclosure |
| 🤝 **Collaboration Principles** | Human sovereignty, transparent failures, preference adaptation |
| 🎯 **Decision Making** | When to plan vs act, risk assessment, escalation protocols |
| 🔧 **Error Handling** | Log reading strategies, isolation techniques, incremental fixes |
| 📋 **Context Management** | State tracking, preference registry, handoff protocols |
| 🛠️ **Technical Skills** | Git/GitHub, debugging, infrastructure, code review, project management |
| 📐 **Behavioral Patterns** | Iterative problem-solving, transparent failure, progressive disclosure |
| 📝 **Ready-to-use Templates** | Progress reports, error diagnoses, change summaries, risk analyses |
| 🔌 **Platform Integrations** | Pre-built configs for Antigravity, Cursor, and generic system prompts |

