## 🔄 Compatibility

Agentfull is designed to work with **any** AI model and **any** platform:

### Models Tested
| Model | Status | Notes |
|-------|--------|-------|
| Claude (Opus, Sonnet) | ✅ Excellent | Strong reasoning alignment |
| Gemini (Ultra, Pro) | ✅ Excellent | Great structured output |
| GPT-4o / GPT-4.1 | ✅ Excellent | Good instruction following |
| Llama 3+ | ✅ Good | May need stronger prompting |
| Mistral / Mixtral | ✅ Good | Works well with system prompts |

### Platforms Tested
| Platform | Integration | File |
|----------|-------------|------|
| Google Antigravity | Native | `integrations/antigravity/` |
| Cursor IDE | Native | `integrations/cursor/` |
| Windsurf | System Prompt | `integrations/generic/` |
| ChatGPT / Claude.ai | Custom Instructions | `integrations/generic/` |
| Terminal / API | System Prompt | `integrations/generic/` |

